title: Crimson Metal Episode II-PLAZA
description:
Crimson Metal - Episode II (c) Madbox Entertainment

Release Date: 07/2017 Protection: Discs: 1 Genre: Violent

As the lone survivor of omega squad Adam Crimson, you continue your
way to freedom through the darkest catacombs of the secret METACORP
labs. KEY FEATURES: New 8 Levels New Enemies New Challenges
For more info go to: http://store.steampowered.com/app/614620/

1. Extract release
2. Mount ISO
3. Install the game
4. Play!

NOTES: This release is standalone and also includes Episode 1 with
the Soundtrack

To start Episode 1, go to the base game dir and run the .exe
CRIMSON METALCRIMSON METAL - EPISODE I.exe
